definition: orchid (蘭花|兰花 Cymbidium goeringii)/fragrant thoroughwort (蘭草|兰草 Eupatorium fortunei)/lily magnolia (木蘭|木兰)
surname Lan/abbr. for Lanzhou 蘭州|兰州[Lan2 zhou1], Gansu

sentences.english: Franz took the lamp, and entered the subterranean grotto, followed by Gaetano.
sentences.chinese: 弗蘭茲拿着火把走進了地下巖洞，後面跟着蓋太諾。

sentences.english: And now, my dear Franz, let us talk of something else.
sentences.chinese: 現在，親愛的弗蘭茲，我們來談些別的吧。
